Title: Quantum Instantons and Quantum Chaos
Authors: H. Jirari and H. Kr√∂ger and X. Q. Luo and K. J. M. Moriarty and S. G. Rubin
Abstract: Based on a closed form expression for the path integral of quantum transition amplitudes, we suggest rigorous definitions of both, quantum instantons and quantum chaos. As an example we compute the quantum instanton of the double well potential.
